==English==
===Noun===
'''arithmetic series''' (''plural'' '''arithmetic series''') <!--plural is the same as the singular-->

#{{analysis}} A [[series]] in which each term except the first is obtained from the previous by adding a [[constant]] value, known as the [[common difference]] of the series.

